songs.lyrics:
I wanna be the one who's always watching your back; I'll protect you, I'll do anything to do that

I wanna be the one who you will always turn to, Oh! I do all of this, so he'd say, "I Love You."

Ohh!... To be the one who's holding onto you so tight

I'm gonna be you Island baby, I'm gonna be your Rock. (×3)

I'm gonna be you Island baby (×2)

When its late at night..., To be the one who's lying by your side. Ohh!...

When its late at night...Oh!..., To be the one who's holding onto you so tight...Ohh!...

To Be The One....
songs.title: Be The One - Gonna be your Island Baby, I’m gonna be your Rock!
